container.value: 中国北京市海淀区紫竹院81号院3号楼2层206-204

creator: Beijing Xiaowei Cloud Service Technology Co., Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
CalendarTask, no procrastination, efficient life

1. Tasks can be synchronized between mobile phones, computers, and iPad platforms
2. It is convenient to view the lunar calendar, solar terms, holidays, and statutory holidays
3. The computer terminal can be transparently displayed on the computer desktop
4. Repeat tasks and reminders can be set
5. Countdown days, provide 5 kinds of cards (birthday, exam, anniversary, festival, default) and can be set as widgets
6. Powerful calendar settings, you can change the color, size, number of rows displayed, etc.
7. The free widget function is convenient for viewing tasks on the desktop of the mobile phone
9. Provide a list mode to display tasks to facilitate quick browsing of your tasks

All of the above functions are available for free


Member function

1. It can automatically synchronize tasks in real time between mobile phones, computers, and iPad platforms
2. History records are automatically backed up, viewed, and deleted
3. The sub-account function can record the content of work, life and study separately
4. Unfinished tasks can be set to be automatically extended within a week
5. Online device management, you can view and operate offline client online devices
6. With the same account, there is no limit to the number of logged-in client devices, and you can log in at home, in the company, anywhere
descriptionShort: Multi-terminal synchronization, schedule management, task reminder,Countdown
